{"tid":2206634,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"大家得個知字 鄭紀航法官嘅判決令大家知道佢係彰顯唔到正義","createTime":"2020-09-17T14:55:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T15:03:52.000Z","uid":70846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"969915d42eb597274b8aac1430f8fb73b7411844","tid":2206634,"uid":70846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T14:55:31.000Z","msg":"鄭官一個月政治case 手足就全部有問題 藍屍警察就無問題<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vMLSiky.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvMLSiky.jpg&h=295c46d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n法官斥被告在錄影會面的說法謊話連篇，亦與辯方在審訊時向控方證人指出的案情不符。不過綜合以上觀察，法官認為學警證供各有版本，難以確信所有證人，特別是學警馬寶權，把事實真相告知法庭。他指未能倚賴學警證供，終裁定警長四項罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/學堂警長被控騙學警-24-萬脫罪-法官-警長謊話連篇-證人亦無告知法庭全部真相/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%AD%B8%E5%A0%82%E8%AD%A6%E9%95%B7%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E9%A8%99%E5%AD%B8%E8%AD%A6-24-%E8%90%AC%E8%84%AB%E7%BD%AA-%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%98-%E8%AD%A6%E9%95%B7%E8%AC%8A%E8%A9%B1%E9%80%A3%E7%AF%87-%E8%AD%89%E4%BA%BA%E4%BA%A6%E7%84%A1%E5%91%8A%E7%9F%A5%E6%B3%95%E5%BA%AD%E5%85%A8%E9%83%A8%E7%9C%9F%E7%9B%B8%2F&d=sV3HumZuViP2rFeoL7TNOICLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=83456531\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%AD%B8%E5%A0%82%E8%AD%A6%E9%95%B7%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E9%A8%99%E5%AD%B8%E8%AD%A6-24-%E8%90%AC%E8%84%AB%E7%BD%AA-%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%98-%E8%AD%A6%E9%95%B7%E8%AC%8A%E8%A9%B1%E9%80%A3%E7%AF%87-%E8%AD%89%E4%BA%BA%E4%BA%A6%E7%84%A1%E5%91%8A%E7%9F%A5%E6%B3%95%E5%BA%AD%E5%85%A8%E9%83%A8%E7%9C%9F%E7%9B%B8%2F&h=ad73ba12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/學堂警長被控騙學警-24-萬脫罪-法官-警長謊話連篇-證人亦無告知法庭全部真相/</a>"},{"pid":"31e654e5b88bed0dfd05f06230411ea40f7f833b","tid":2206634,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T15:02:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/